name: La Garza y el Siervo (Homenaje a María Félix)
description:
A homage to María Félix: Mexican actress, OG Diva and force of nature. Digital triptych with her masculine animus and details of her totems: a Lizard necklace and a Machete.

1080x1080 Frame-by-Frame linocut animation with digital intervention. 8 editions minted as a GIF commemorating her day of birth (April 8, 1914) and death (April 8, 2002).

Dedicated to my mom who is 81 years strong and still enjoying La Doña films on TCM.
